生动描绘商品视角、光影、微小道具，制造呼吸感。例如："The product is captured from a sharp 45-degree professional studio angle, showcasing its exquisite texture. It is placed elegantly amidst natural scene elements like scattered fresh cotton soft petals and gentle water ripples under a cinematic lighting setup. Soft rim light outlines the product edges, accompanied by precise, diffuse physical shadows that anchor the product onto the surface, creating an authentic 8k commercial photography look."

5. Clean Marketing Copywriting (纯净高转化模块文案 - 绝对隔离)
**前置判定：上游标注图片无文案则本整段直接省略，不输出任何标题、副标题、项目符号内容；有文案才执行下方规则。**
这里是唯一的文案渲染区域。为了防止 AI 误将格式词画入图中，必须使用最干净的英文段落直接陈述。严禁出现字重、像素、冒号等排版提示词：
